-LIVE- Weekday Mornings 7:00am – 9:00am ET

Streaming encore of any program from the last week on demand: Click Here to Choose and Listen

WHKY Radio’s morning live, local talkshow. Hosted by Hal Row, First Talk airs LIVE weekday mornings 7:00am until 9:00am ET. Get all the local news, sports, weather and information. Call us at 828/ 485-5508 and express your opinion live on-air about the morning’s topic or ask a question of our in-studio guest
